des:
AMIBOT HOME products help you control home appliance. You can simply ask Alexa to control your robot vacuum cleaner.

After connecting Alexa to your AMIBOT HOME products in a few simple steps:
1. Download "AMIBOT HOME" app in android or ios app market;
2. Register one tuya account in "AMIBOT HOME" app;
3. You need to have some AMIBOT devices in hand;
4. Configure the device in "AMIBOT HOME" app and change appropriate name for your devices which will be used in "AMIBOT HOME" skills;
5. Download Amazon "Alexa" app from android, ios or Amazon app market;
6. Configure Echo with "Alexa" app;
7. Search "AMIBOT HOME" skill from the "Alexa" app skills category;
8. Click Enable skill of "AMIBOT HOME", and you'll be navigated to "AMIBOT HOME" login page;
9. Input your AMIBOT HOME account username and password, you'll be redirect to the success page;
10. Now all setup is finished.

You can enjoy the voice control on your home device like these:
“Alexa, turn on the robot.”
“Alexa, turn off the robot.”
